query:
/*+  */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 100 AND q1.view_count <= 100000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('alternative-proof',
'book-recommendation',
'hdmi',
'indicator',
'lie-algebras',
'nonlinear-optimization',
'partial-derivative',
'sobolev-spaces',
'ssd',
'text-processing')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 10 AND u1.reputation <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu',
'math')
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Analytical',
'Cleanup',
'Deputy',
'Disciplined',
'Generalist',
'Great Question',
'Populist',
'Reviewer',
'Steward',
'Strunk & White',
'Tag Editor',
'Talkative',
'Taxonomist',
'Tenacious')
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
